ow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":304}],"windowDisplayName":"夏希","body":"他們在那邊的攤位套圈圈。先別說這個了，你看這件皮革外套，\n我在剛剛運動場的跳蚤市場買的。\n紅色是不是超級帥氣？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":304,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":304,"voiceId":"event228-04-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"哈哈哈，這嗨過頭了吧？\n這種華麗鮮艷的皮革外套要在哪種場合穿啊？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event228-04-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":304}],"windowDisplayName":"夏希","body":"不不不，要比嗨的話我就輸給沙綾了。\n你手上拿著那袋鼓起來的零食，\n到底是逛了多少攤？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":304,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":304,"voiceId":"event228-04-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"哈哈哈……總覺得每一攤看起來都很好吃，一不小心就……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event228-04-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkChara